  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Next generation sequencing (including targeted gene seqeuncing, exome and transcriptome
      sequencing) will be performed from fresh frozen tumor samples to understand the genetic
      alteration of tumors and to aid in optimal selection of further therapeutic agents.
    </textblock>
